                  <handDesc>
                     <p>The diagonal strokes after 1/3 may represent an additional fraction, perhaps 1/4; 1/6 seems less likely since 1/3 1/6 = 1/2.  The curvature of the third sign in the season name favors peret over shemw.</p>
